# === Feature Interaction Types ===

[test::features::NonEmptyWithForwarding]
description=std::string; non_empty, <=>, no-constexpr
forward=size, empty, clear, length

[test::features::PositiveWithCast]
description=int; positive, cast<double>, cast<long>

[test::features::BoundedWithHash]
